An open source Bitcoin client library built using Java and implements the Bitcoin network protocol.

The project was announced on March 7, 2011 (1.1).  The project was built by a Google employee as a "20 percent time" project (1.2).

##See Also

* [[Bitcoin-android]] mobile client

* [[Bitcoin_Wallet_for_Android]] - a standalone wallet for Android devices (based on BitCoinJ)

